[African Swine Fever continues to be a big problem in West Africa.
The outbreak area is close to that reported a few years previously by
Tayo Babalola of the University of Ibadan. He also recently sent in
information about an outbreak in Ghana. Such reporting is very much
appreciated. - Mod.PC]
